{"tid":301335,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[真FF迷應該試下] 呢度冇人玩FFRK?","createTime":"2017-06-28T14:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T15:09:59.000Z","uid":100155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f30aa0e6e2ce7a0b2fd8a785d3c0182d1eeb991","tid":301335,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多代FF人物全部有得用唔洗抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加埋FF各代神曲bgm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好enjoyable<br />\n戰鬥要諗唔同角色配搭,每個角色放咩技能同戰略<br />\n人物又極平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會一個角色/一team角色組合屌打所有野<br />\n同埋抽係抽技，所以鐘意ge角色又唔會被其他新角色取代 <br />\n每隻角色ge技都好有特色，同埋定位唔係單純分tank, mage, 物理，補師咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩落就知   <br />\n而角色ge技同佢地喺本身自己果代遊戲入面嘅故事/做過嘅野有關（e.g. Kefak 有招burst係放毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  Celes係魔封劍   FF5 Faris有招技係召換自己隻水龍射d箭出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n戰鬥又係FF傳統ge ATB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 畫面同人物全部做到係FF6果隻點陣style   <br />\n登場作品&amp;人物連FFT, FFTA, FF15, 零式, crisis core, 10-2, FF4續集, FF14果啲都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前覺得手遊都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  體力制／刷素材 (FGO果d) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   係得card game好玩d   但玩過呢隻之後改觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩左一年覺得仲係好有新鮮感 因為隻game 幾日就update 加FF人物之餘 耐唔耐就有全新ge系統玩  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國reddit討論：<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/FFRecordKeeper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FFFRecordKeeper%2F&d=kds1GbL7MBeVrdR55ugcw7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=a5f4020a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com/r/FFRecordKeeper/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/221025_639c6d101d0291f2f41c54f2eb76e9e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F221025_639c6d101d0291f2f41c54f2eb76e9e1.png&h=fc56a3a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/221026_eef7a370836405c69bf35076290525bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F221026_eef7a370836405c69bf35076290525bf.png&h=31309da2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/221026_4e0cfb0c478c1969b8b8064f95c9c277.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F221026_4e0cfb0c478c1969b8b8064f95c9c277.png&h=558745cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/221027_ba01f27dda9292f65f60c40b0eecba2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F221027_ba01f27dda9292f65f60c40b0eecba2c.png&h=2409d0d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/221027_6bd35929d0b4264abba8ca704c0c0365.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F221027_6bd35929d0b4264abba8ca704c0c0365.png&h=2a350ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/221027_182b411a8de33a468060